    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesnt feel like a gift though. it feels like i'm just draining them. every time i struggle or i can't get things together, i see it in their eyes. they're growing up in this constant fog of my instability. i keep thinking... if i wasn't even in the picture, they could actually have a chance to be happy without worrying about me all the time. wouldn't it be more selfless to just get out of their way?",
